c":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3210,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/05\/16\/ghusl-before-jumuah\/","url_meta":{"origin":36650,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Ghusl: Perform ritual bath before Friday prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 16, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Sa\u2019id al-Khudri reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cTaking a bath on Friday is a duty upon every person who has reached the age of puberty.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 839,\u00a0S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 846 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0(authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15810,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/08\/23\/hour-dua-friday\/","url_meta":{"origin":36650,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Jumuah: Special hour for Friday supplications","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 23, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, mentioned the day of Friday and he said, \u201cIn it is a moment in which no Muslim stands to pray and ask Allah for something but that he will be given it,\"\u00a0and he indicated with his hand\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3213,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/05\/16\/no-talking-jumuah-khutbah\/","url_meta":{"origin":36650,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Khutbah: Not allowed to speak during Friday Sermon","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 16, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cIf you tell your companion to be quiet on Friday while the Imam is speaking, you have spoken improperly.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 892, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 851 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim Al-Nawawi\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25635,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/12\/19\/ghusl-once-seven-days\/","url_meta":{"origin":36650,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Ghusl: Take a bath at least once a week","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 19, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cIt is a duty for Allah upon every Muslim to perform a ritual bath at least once every seven days, washing his head and his body.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 856, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 849 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/w